{"1627850":{"success":true,"data":{"type":"game","name":"Deadly Broadcast","steam_appid":1627850,"required_age":0,"is_free":false,"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<h1>DISCORD CHANNEL<\/h1><p><a href=\"https:\/\/steamcommunity.com\/linkfilter\/?url=https:\/\/discord.gg\/Ds3e5XKVXm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  ><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/1627850\/extras\/discordserver.png?t=1657097043\" \/><\/a><\/p><br><h1>About the Game<\/h1>Cameras are ready. Lenses are set! Batteries are full. So let the broadcast begin! <br>Unbeknownst you enter the old mental hospital to make a fun broadcast for your followers but to all, nothing goes as you expect it to go. You must find a way out of here with the help of your teammates and instant live messages from your viewers!<br><br><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/1627850\/extras\/1.gif?t=1657097043\" \/>   <img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/1627850\/extras\/2.gif?t=1657097043\" \/><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Gather Your Team!<\/h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Online co-op for 2-4 players<br><\/li><li>Work as a team to destroy hearts and evade devils intent on killing you. Remember everyone should be saved and the longer you stay in the hospital the worse things will get.<\/li><\/ul><br><br><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/1627850\/extras\/kizson.gif?t=1657097043\" \/>     <img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/1627850\/extras\/kaslison.gif?t=1657097043\" \/><br><br><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/1627850\/extras\/youtuberson.gif?t=1657097043\" \/>    <img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/1627850\/extras\/siskoson.gif?t=1657097043\" \/><br><br><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/1627850\/extras\/ezgif-2-8fff8e8ba6.gif?t=1657097043\" \/><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Single Player Mode<\/h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>